node.text:
The new @aventi A11-05 Emerald REC🔥

A mesmerizing and complicated timepiece that features a 68 facet case (a brilliant cut diamond has 58 facets) in a super cool material called Emerald REC.

The watch also features a dual barrel Flying tourbillon movement with 72h of power reserve. Everything is on display through the skeletonized dial 👌🏼

node.text:
State of the art gemsetting skills by @jacobandco 💎

The Caviar Flying Tourbillon collection embodies @jacobandco’s drive to stop at nothing in its quest to create masterpieces of incomparable beauty.

This is the Blue Sapphire Baguette version with 424 sapphires (~44.35cts). Limited to 18 pieces.

node.text:
Behind the scenes of crafting the @jacobandco Opera Godfather 💎

The Opera Godfather comes in a 49mm rose gold or black ceramic and domed sapphire crystal case, the large size allowing for the placement of two barrels hand-set with 666 brilliant white diamonds (approx. 1.85 cts) specially crafted to reproduce the music.

The triple axis tourbillon dances it’s round-the-clock mechanical ballet.
Limited edition of 88 pieces  and priced at $420,000 💸
